    "synopsis": "Ten thousand years after their Primarch's murder, the Night Lords endure as scattered raiders, feared and hunted across the galaxy. Talos, a battle-brother of First Claw and a reluctant prophet cursed with his gene-father's visions, fights to keep his fractured warband alive as it is drawn into one of Abaddon the Despoiler's black crusades against the forge world of Crythe. When Talos returns from a vision with a captured Navigator and new servitors, he provokes the wrath of the warband's tyrannical master — and sets First Claw on a collision course with the Mechanicus, the Black Legion, and the legion's own ruin.",
